## Revision pass: 2026-07-17 (my_feedback_v2 §5 artifact-hygiene cleanup)

### Problem addressed
Prior build had PRETRAINED=True loading from .pkl files that were committed or
pre-generated by make_assets. On a fresh Colab (empty assets/), the notebook
would fail with FileNotFoundError because there was no "generate if absent" fallback.
Also: static PNG fallbacks (nb0_fig_trophy.png, nb0_fig_overfit.png) were saved
to assets/ and displayed on exception — per §5 these must not exist; figures must
always render live from data.

### Changes to jax-examples/src_00_caixa_de_ferramentas.py

  1. Setup cell:
     - ASSETS.mkdir(exist_ok=True, parents=True) added — creates dir if absent.
     - Added helper functions: carregar_pkl, salvar_pkl, _checkpoints_ok
       (matching NB01 pattern for consistency).
     - Added compact Adam helpers (adam_init, adam_passo) for fast fallback generation.
     - Improved ASSETS path fallback: if ../assets doesn't sit under jax-examples/,
       fall back to /tmp/nb00_assets (true Colab safety net).

  2. Data generation cell:
     - Removed plt.savefig(ASSETS / "nb0_fig_senoide_intro.png") — not needed; figure
       renders live.
     - Added xg_in = jnp.array(x_grade_norm, ...).reshape(-1, 1) — moved here from
       the trophy figure cell so it is always defined regardless of trophy figure flow.

  3. Training cell (normal FCNN) — restructured to three-branch pattern:
     - Branch 1 (fast, default): _checkpoints_ok(*CKPT_NORMAL) → carregar_pkl (load)
     - Branch 2 (first run, PRETRAINED=True, no cache): trains with Adam 1000 steps,
       saves epoch 0/200/500/1000 checkpoints, uses jax.jit for speed.
     - Branch 3 (PRETRAINED=False, demo mode): trains with SGD 1000 epochs, saves
       all intermediate checkpoints, uses jax.jit for speed.

  4. Trophy figure cell:
     - Removed try/except and static PNG fallback (nb0_fig_trophy.png).
     - Changed open(ASSETS/fname) to carregar_pkl(fname) for consistency.
     - Removed xg_in definition (moved to data generation cell).
     - Figure now always renders live from loaded/computed params.

  5. Overfit cell — restructured to three-branch pattern (same as training cell):
     - Branch 1 (fast): _checkpoints_ok("nb0_overfit_params.pkl") → carregar_pkl
     - Branch 2 (first run, PRETRAINED=True): Adam 5000 steps, lr=0.005, jit.
     - Branch 3 (PRETRAINED=False): SGD 5000 epochs, jit.
     - Removed try/except and static PNG fallback (nb0_fig_overfit.png) from
       comparison figure block.

### Changes to jax-examples/utils/make_assets_00_caixa_de_ferramentas.py

  - Docstring updated: script is now labeled OPTIONAL (notebook self-generates).
  - PNG generation removed: nb0_fig_trophy.png and nb0_fig_overfit.png are no longer
    generated (figures always render live; static PNGs are not used).
  - Checkpoint generation retained: still generates all 5 pkl files with Adam for
    best visual quality if run before the notebook.
  - matplotlib import still present (used as Agg backend guard); import kept.

